🍰🍫🍩𝒜 ℬℯ𝒶𝓇𝓎 𝒮𝓌ℯℯ𝓉 𝒯ℯ𝒶 ℬ𝓇ℯ𝒶𝓀 ! Because you just need to do one thing that makes you happy everyday and life will be a bit more bear-able. 😂

Tried this Chocolate Mousse 🐻 Cake and it was a tad on the sweet side. But cake always complements Earl Grey and that's what I had to wash some of that sugar down.

We are on Day 44 already and almost seeing the light at the end of the tunnel. Hang in there everyone!
